{"tid":2368823,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭松泰：如果你以為自己好撚鍾意香港，但你無睇過呢一本書嘅話，你應該好好反省自己對唔對得住手足？","createTime":"2021-01-16T14:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T04:32:58.000Z","uid":271829,"like":4,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6c39c930144b0cc9afaaec5a5b2be82d2969e213","tid":2368823,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T14:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vk2VQtE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVk2VQtE.jpg&h=91b05dd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n熱血公民鄭松泰：<br />\n如果你以為自己好撚鍾意香港，但你無睇過呢一本書嘅話，你應該好好反省自己對唔對得住手足？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20201229/s00002/1609180486585/團結基金《香港志》出首冊-稱「述而不論」無意洗腦\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20201229%2Fs00002%2F1609180486585%2F%E5%9C%98%E7%B5%90%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E3%80%8A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%BF%97%E3%80%8B%E5%87%BA%E9%A6%96%E5%86%8A-%E7%A8%B1%E3%80%8C%E8%BF%B0%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E8%AB%96%E3%80%8D%E7%84%A1%E6%84%8F%E6%B4%97%E8%85%A6&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=ea6302b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20201229%2Fs00002%2F1609180486585%2F%E5%9C%98%E7%B5%90%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E3%80%8A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%BF%97%E3%80%8B%E5%87%BA%E9%A6%96%E5%86%8A-%E7%A8%B1%E3%80%8C%E8%BF%B0%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E8%AB%96%E3%80%8D%E7%84%A1%E6%84%8F%E6%B4%97%E8%85%A6&h=97f5e345\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20201229/s00002/1609180486585/團結基金《香港志》出首冊-稱「述而不論」無意洗腦</a><br />\n...<br />\n【明報專訊】由團結香港基金成立、負責編修《香港志》的「香港地方志中心」（下稱中心），昨出版首冊《總述 大事記》，簡介本港上至新石器時代，下至2017年7月1日的6500多項大事。中心願景提到讓港人「了解香港與國家、中華民族與生俱來的血脈親情」，而特首林鄭月娥及中聯辦主任駱惠寧擔任中心的名譽贊助人。中心強調負責編志的學者編輯自主，過程不受任何事左右，中心亦沒有意圖「洗腦」。<br />\n..."},{"pid":"5d8d80dc15fc820362e4a5bccf3bfaedb9cb88d8","tid":2368823,"uid":89608,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01